<br>
Pages 1 &amp; 2<br>
<br>
Nukes, Gate, Malo, Cadeau, Boon.<br>
<br>
Pages 3 &amp; 4<br>
<br>
Shielding, Armor, Resists, Vocerates and Dyzils, Transons Infusion and Summon Companion.<br>
<br>
Page 5 &amp; 6<br>
<br>
Common Summons, CotH, Muzzle.<br>
<br>
Page 7 &amp; 8<br>
<br>
Invis, See Invis, Bind, Banish, Secondary nukes like Banish Summoned, Maelstrom and such.<br>
<br>
Page 9 &amp; 10<br>
<br>
Less used summons, utility spells, lower mana cost malisment for when i'm soloing, spells I like to goof around with.<br>
<br>
Skip 15-20 pages to older spells arranged essentially in reverse order.  As I remove spells from use they are moved back.<br>
