<br>
Page 1&amp;2<br>
Archshielding<br>
Phantom Plate<br>
Gate<br>
Damage Shield<br>
Invis<br>
Shock of Swords<br>
Cinderbolt<br>
Blaze<br>
Elemental Maelstrom<br>
<br>
99% of the time when I die, I can sit down, and re-mem all my spells all from the same page...  At most I turn 1 page to load up a pet and coldstone summon.<br>
<br>
All my outdated spells (lower lvl pets, older shielding spells, lower DD's) get moved to the back of the book.<br>
<br>
